Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In 1996 after Id Software dropped Quake and John Romero,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.16,0:00:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,they were looking to go in another direction with their next project,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.88,0:00:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Which wasn't always gonna be called Quake II
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There were other ideas for the title like "WOR" with an "O",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but everybody just decided to call it Quake II,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite the fact that it has nothing to do with the first game.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As explained by Tim Willits, Id co-owner and designer for, uh... 25 years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.42,0:00:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The first Quake game was kind of a mess to develop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and so everyone decided to have a clearer vision of what the game should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.78,0:01:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sc-fi! Space marines!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.51,0:01:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, this was 1997 and the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.18,0:01:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"big, tough space marine" trope hadn't been worn quite as thin:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.26,0:01:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,one man fighting against an army of horrible villains.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,An inspiration cited by the devs was The Guns of Navarone,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.90,0:01:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,a movie about a unit of commandos in WWII
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,sent to destroy artillery so that the British Navy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,could rescue trapped soldiers from the Germans
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.36,0:01:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen it; the movie is older than my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.74,0:01:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, after referencing The Cabinet of Dr. Caligari
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.58,0:01:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in a video about DOS trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.68,0:01:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So the story of Quake II,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.16,0:01:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,don't get too excited, there's still barely story in this game
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,takes its cues from WWII and not HP Lovecraft
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.44,0:01:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and from the beginning it was gonna be a more
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.90,0:01:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,focused, polished, impressive game than its predecessor,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,which is funny because Quake II is probably remembered less fondly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.56,0:01:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Quake 1 had a certain spirit; an atmosphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.68,0:01:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,certainly helped by Trent Reznor's soundtrack
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Trent Reznor was asked to come back and refused after seeing the game itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,saying something i've seen reported as the charitable
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:02:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Quake 2 was a turning point for Id Software, I think,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,where the scrappy little company that made deeply influential games
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.88,0:02:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,became a real company,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,With like, responsible employees.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, dedicated people who lacked the cult of personality that would surround others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention Tom Hall and John Romero were off at Ion Storm,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandy Peterson moved on to Ensemble Studios
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfected human analogue and Jace Hall asphyxiator, John Carmack
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"I would be going to strangle from the rear."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"That was the weirdest sensation I've ever had in my whole life, did you get that on camera?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"That was awesome dude"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's a good thing you didn't wet your pants"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Carmack did the thing where he made a new engine,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.94,0:02:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,or, more of an avancement of the previous one that made it a bit more colourful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But he didn't do skeletal animations,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,what the fuck was he thinking there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Adrian Carmack and American McGee were still around
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But this was a different Id Software.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there time had come and gone when it came to truly revolutionising things
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A year later would bring Half-Life, and also Unreal,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,which was built as a "Quake killer" when it started,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think it succeeded. I find it's a better Quake II than Quake II is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:03:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not as familiar with Quake 2; I haven't played it as much as Quake, or Doom, or Doom 3,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,or probably even Wolfenstein 3D.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was genuinely curious what playing on the hardest skill would be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Vanilla Quake 2 doesn't let you select the hardest skill,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,skill 3, also known as hard+.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thankfully Yamagi Quake II, the port I'm using, calls it nightmare and lets you select it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This, I feel, helps the game significantly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I would often get bored around Ammo Depot and drop the game entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've beaten it before, hell, Quake 2 was the first game I ever deathmatched online in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The deathmatch is superb.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll remember where the railgun in The Edge is until I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard+ it is, because it can't possibly be as degrading as
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,being constantly gibbed by someone named Slimshady99xx
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard+ is like hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but the enemies don't flinch, they attack faster and have more health.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the time I didn't even notice, except here:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, fuck that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway I think it's time to start this less than strange journey into Id's dark age.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not to say Quake II isn't a bad game, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:04:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's exactly what I would expect from every Id game that came after it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,until Doom 2016, and then Doom Eternal
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Doom Eternal is so slick and intricate and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine the company being able to make a game as impressive again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Where Doom 2016 was an evolution of Id's formula,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Doom Eternal was a redefinition of everything we thought could be done with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Quake 2 is probably the least that can be done with it:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,a technical marvel that is a good action game;
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,a well-oiled machine fueled by blood and explosions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And if Quake 2 is the worst game your studio would put out then, man, that's fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But RAGE is worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy when we get to RAGE...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"Our radio tower up on the hill stopped working. We need someone to fix it."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Eh, probably just out of alignment."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"You get it fixed for me, and I'll give you a shotgun. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"This should be an easy job."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"Well, not bad, stranger!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, can we talk about the soundtrack first?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's BEAUTIFUL.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not ambient Trent Reznor nightmare fuel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard, fast, wonderful metal. The stuff Bobby Prince wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Except now they can put it on a CD and play it in-game!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's soooo good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was made by Sonic Mayhem, which is a person who's name is..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not even going to try and pronounce that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of those soundtracks you can pop into your CD player,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,(A thing we used to do)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And listen to it *without* the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It absolutely shreds, adds so much to the action.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The basic story of Quake II is that you are Bitterman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that, a named protagonist!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And your pod crashes onto Stroggos, planet of the Stroggs
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A sinister race of aliens that fuses human or alien tissue with metal,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,like The Borg but bloodier and more savage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,..and with explosions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And only one of these monsters has a shield
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Your main objective, out of all the other ones that gentle nag you throughout the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is to destroy the Big Gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is to destroy the BIG Gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is to destroy the BIG GUN.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,After you've made your way through military installations,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the city, other military installations, the palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Quake II doesn't have a lot of variety in it's settings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It does what it can with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.76,0:06:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In terms of level design it has a kind of Hexen-like hub system
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that lets you travel back-and-forth between areas
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not used extensively for anything important, you go to this map,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,then complete an objective that opens up an area on the previous map,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,go there, and by the time you're done
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you might not even know you completed the mission
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,because everything you need to do is fairly obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I've played it too much, but the objectives seem to complete themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,while you're battle the Strogg
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's never confusing, which I guess is a testament to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the level designers, seasoned pros by this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The first hub starts off as soon as you crash and escape your pod
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,here you are, armed with only a shitty little blaster,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,shooting the common low-level hitscanners.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,..for like a minute until you come over here and get the shotgun
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a bad shotgun, I always liked the look of it, even if it felt a little weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the game teaches you that there's breakable glass now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You can crouch, there's going to be a robot voice telling you..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"COMPUTER UPDATED"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,..every time your mission status changes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You know immediately that this isn't Quake 1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you were lucky enough to have one of those fancy 3D accelerator cards at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't gonna look like Quake 1 either!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,even in software mode the new lighting and particle effects were pretty impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Quake 2 RTX is kinda trash, though
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:08:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it runs badly and ruins the atmosphere Trent Reznor said that this game doesn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Default settings make everything really bright
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and when you turn that down you still have to deal with texture bugs
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and WHAT THE FUCK DID THEY DO TO MY RAILGUN? :<
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all very shiny and suffers from
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,adding HD textures to a game that wasn't designed for them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,..at least it doesn't cost anything
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Another new thing is an Inventory system
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The first inventory item you'll pick up is a silencer..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the game has *useful* powerups, too. Quad Damage, Invulnerability,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,a Toxin Suit.. which is useful in about 3 places throughout the whole game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A power shield too.. and I think that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.56,0:08:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,..yeah, I save the powerups for when I need them, mostly for cheesing bosses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too bad you don't get nearly the number of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Quad Damage power-ups as you do in Quake 1
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,rampages are a lot less frequent,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I had maybe one or two during the whole game, and it seems like a complete non-factor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it was in Doom 2016, where you just pick up a few during the whole campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Quake II does have an atmosphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,a foreboding sci-fi body horror thing going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Space Nazis made of flesh and metal to keep the Guns of Navarone influences
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemies may not flinch,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but they still do this thing where they continue attacking as they die,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,which you can avoid by gibbing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They all gib.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,THEY ALL GIB!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,.. it's *actually* pretty cool
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're moving along through this base shooting Strogg
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,who wont give you much trouble 'till the Enforcers
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Chaingunners? :< Fun..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Slightly less of a problem when get the Machine Gun in the next level
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,which has recoil for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...what game do you think you are Quake 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut that shit out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still satisfying, because the game gives it to you super early
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and lets you mow down the lower enemies with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not what we're here for, we need to go to the secret level..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,once you get through the sewer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a swim, go down this elevator
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and your objective changes from "Go to a thing loosely related to saving humanity" to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"Find a powerful weapon".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,..and oh boy do you ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Quake 2's Super Shotgun lives up to the family legacy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pump action now, it sounds just as devastating as the Doom 2 Super Shotgun
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.68,0:10:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This should clarify that all the weapons in this game are not a problem
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, they don't have any muzzle flashes for some goddamn reason, but whatever I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pick up throwable grenades, too
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,which I don't really use. I like to save them until I get the Grenade Launcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In Hard+ mode you'll meet the two most dangerous enemies in the game in the first hub.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugghh, this one always weirded me out
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.68,0:11:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll suck your health dry with..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Euughh..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Gunner, who really only becomes a huge problem on Hard+
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,because he attacks faster
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't know if he's going to spam me with machine gun fire or grenades.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Early game you might benefit from crouching under the grenades if you're close enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I really prefer getting the Rocket Launcher or Railgun to deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that you have the Super Shotgun..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to point out that none of this is "bad design", it checks all the boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your enemies all make distinct sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and movements that provide proper feedback to the player
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You walk into a room, you hear something, you know what's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"Trespasser!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, the Berserker's are like kittens they're mostly harmless
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Their attack windup takes so long that it's your own fault if you get hit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You meet a few other monsters in the first hub, the fliers, the barracuda sharks,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,easily dealt with with the Super Shotgun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think any of the monsters besides the Gunner or the Parasite actually annoy me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,they're not too difficult to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemies have some really cool idle animations too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,..be really hard to see them in-game with all the shooting, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,0.o
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name, scumbag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"Trespasser!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Did your parents have any children that lived!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh shit, wait.. that is a dead guy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what? Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember when I said I usually stop playing this game
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,around Ammo Depot because I get bored?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well second hub starts with Ammo Depot,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm trying to remember why
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You get the Chaingun around here and that's fun
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,even if it chews through your ammo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe *because* it chews through your ammo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember an FPS game before this that let you spit so much lead at an enemy at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of amazing even if it is impractical.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:13:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But sometimes, just everyone now and then you run into a room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and gib everything in it by firing 200 bullets in about 5 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty satisfying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always around here that the game starts to lose me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is it that I've already dealt with it's most difficult challenges?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The game doesn't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason the game thinks that these Tanks are a problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,even though I can spam the chaingun at them and avoid any rockets or energy blasts
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The first boss'd be better served with the Tank name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking about single segments of Quake 2 isn't really that exciting
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,where in other games you'll have specific levels
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and areas where you can consider high points,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Quake 2 feels like it maintains a certain consistency all the way through
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's never bad, but also very little stands out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's talk about the rest of the guns because they're great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grenade Launcher, I think it it feels better than Quake or Quake 3's grenade launcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rocket Launcher? Not quite as good as Quake 1's, but it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hyperblaster has a wind-up for some goddamn reason..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but I find it's a good replacement for the Machine Gun anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your standard rapid fire energy weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The Railgun? Perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow Warrior may have had one first but Quake 2 had it best
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Quake 3 added a sound queue to help the player know when it was ready to fire again
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,which is cool, otherwise it seems like railguns may have peaked with the Quake series.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And the BFG10K, you all know what it is and what it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The first real attempt to upgrade the classic BFG
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to make it not based on hacked-together Doom engine nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a big green ball that now also shoots lasers to nearby targets as it passes by
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,so now you've got what I call "The ID Arsenal",
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the formula that ID games would more or less follow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,until like Doom 2016, give or take a super shotgun or a railgun here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Pistol
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shotgun
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Super Shotgun
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Light automatic weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.74,0:15:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Heavy automatic weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Rocket Launcher
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Rapid fire energy pew-pew gun
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,(Quake 3 has two of those)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,BFG
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,..it's the way it goes, it's like a brand, an ID brand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's what sticks with me most and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,why Quake 2 sometimes leaves a sour taste in my mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,ID became a brand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And while there was a little wiggle room when it came to the formula
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Doom 3 is scary, Rage has 3 side quests..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it feels like there wasn't any room for anything game-changing anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,if it wasn't the technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And that technology lead to games taking longer and longer to make
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Doom 3 took four years, Rage took seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,ID Software is, and will probably forever be tech wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to go into this like other Pro videos
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,here are the enemies, here are the weapons, here's how these work together..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but you already know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a few secret levels to find, Sudden Death is actually pretty unique
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,if you can jump up past this waterfall in Receiving Center
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be taken straight to Sudden Death,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to collect as many powerups and weapons as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,in the small amount of time it gives you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The third secret level, much closer to the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is a low-gravity space station full of flying enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,..it sure is that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hate playing Quake 2 again,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you were to ask me what parts I specifically remember
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell you much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a mine full of Mutants.. three bosses they never caused me much trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and it would be hard for me to really differentiate between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tank thing, flying thing, and the final boss had a BFG and two forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I played through Quake 2, took me about 6 hours minus the time I spent taking notes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,which going over them again couldn't have been very long..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This level always gives me trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,hardest map in the game as far as I'm concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,even when you meet the Iron Maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They can be deal with quickly, a couple rockets or a couple railgun shots,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But these menacing hallways even include a mini sewer section..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,with a Parasite in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.37,0:17:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As-if they predicted that 23 years later some asshole would come along
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and use it for a dumb gag I can't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If I stop doing it the joke falls apart
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,because it relies on me being petty enough to count every single one every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess things liven-up when you get towards the big gun
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and that map with the air strike is cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to disable the supply train that the Strogg are using
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's on that train, or why it's important, it doesnt matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The mission objectives of Quake 2 are effective at
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,portraying a certain scope of the human operations on Stroggos.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a one man army, no-one else can get to the surface until we destroy the big gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And to do that we have to complete all of these secondary objectives
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not entirely sure how this war started in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a little bit in the intro that explains that we were attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The intro has what sounds like news reports explaining that the Strogg attacked major cities
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and that our brave heroes were taking the fight to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a bad setup, make those alien bastards pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of righteous bloodshed that's expressed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in a paragraph in the Doom and Quake manuals
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,as an excuse to kill everything that moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,These cutscenes are a new feature of Quake 2
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,..and I don't think they help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A radio voice gives you objectives and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,between units a computer screen with a similarly robotic voice
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,shows you a map and tells you what you'll being doing later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, the what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.26,0:19:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The 'Str-ah-g'?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.26,0:19:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"As these brave soldiers took the fight to the 'Str-oag's home planet.."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The 'Str-oag'?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...I can't win, I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Calling this game "story-driven" is like calling Jurassic Park "science-driven."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is still the flea circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Adding further context to it only raises more questions
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm working on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's what the whole fucking game is about! It's about the BIG GUN!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It just feels like another sewer..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.06,0:20:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,another maze of pipes, ramps and metal..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, god..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh god, please no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do the Dopefish dirty like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like this! :(
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Towards the end as you're headed into the Palace you find the Tank Commanders,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are upgraded versions of the tanks from earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.18,0:21:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are obviously big bastards who take a lot of your ammo to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tank Commanders are like the elite guards of the Strogg,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it's at the end of this palace level where this happens..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having an interaction with another character
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that isn't just a staticky voice on the other end of
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the radio saying vague army man things at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.08,0:21:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd think getting here would be difficult..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is! Occasionally..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially if you have one of those source ports
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,where the crosshair's are big, blocky, ugly things that hurt my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...fucking disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But this game isn't made to be a dick to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have Spawns or Arch-viles
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing blinds you, or outmaneuvers you, or really challenges you that much..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even the Strogg leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.46,0:21:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm invulnerable for half of the fight, and for the other half I can just run circles around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's better than any of the boss fights in Quake 1, because it's a *boss* fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and most of the Doom ones now that I think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.94,0:22:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This bit at the end with the animation, the torso trying to re-attach to the legs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.12,0:22:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is cool and memorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.44,0:22:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and I feel like the rest of the game rarely lives up to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.54,0:22:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The player is guided through Quake 2 without much resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the game just wants you to dive in and have fun, and dying isn't very fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.62,0:22:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the things I noticed when playing a little of the first Quake 2 expansion by Xatrix
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.76,0:22:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,was that it was significantly more difficult than the main campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.84,0:22:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is true of most expansion packs, but the important part is *why*.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.28,0:22:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're thrown into a sewer level pretty early..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.86,0:22:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And something that vanilla Quake II never really prepared you for
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.60,0:22:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,was an abundance of rudely placed hitscanners.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.02,0:22:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ID Software is made up of professionals
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Who make very deliberate design choices..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.90,0:22:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Xatrix, who up to this point had worked on Redneck Rampage,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.82,0:22:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't care about the players feelings..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.38,0:23:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,For fuck's sake! These introductory enemies, whatever they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.30,0:23:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,leap around like the Mutants and take a solid three to five shells to bring down!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,ID Software, at least in Quake 2, wanted to keep the power fantasy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but like a lot of developers, lost the idea that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.45,0:23:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the fantasy only works if you overcome something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.84,0:23:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,not if you feel like you're operating the machine properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.68,0:23:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The other thing that sticks out in my mind of Quake II probably more than anything else
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the secret developer's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.24,0:23:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a cool Easter Egg, and I really like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.86,0:23:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's more here..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.42,0:23:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What was happening at ID Software during this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.32,0:23:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides the public bitchyness towards Ion Storm and Romero, and Daikatana..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The story to this, of course, is hinted at in Masters of Doom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,down to the easter egg room designed by Tim Willits himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Carmack had dissapeared, locking himself away in coding
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.34,0:23:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and within a year artist Adrian Carmack, no relation, would want out of ID Software
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.50,0:24:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,felling that the company was just making the same game over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,American McGee and Adrian Carmack would be gone soon enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.72,0:24:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,McGee getting the same treatment Romero and Tom Hall got for the most part
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.10,0:24:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you hit Carmack's button..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.24,0:24:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.22,0:24:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,John, John what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.06,0:24:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.28,0:24:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.70,0:24:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it stop.. make it stop..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.90,0:24:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know there's a self-destruct happening and the station is about to explode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.32,0:25:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but that doesn't matter, it's the end of the game and Bitterman survives.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.34,0:25:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Quake 2 runs and plays like one of Carmack's Ferrari's,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.58,0:25:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,impressive, pretty, and powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.98,0:25:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's only so much a car can offer you if you've got a tiny penis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.65,0:00:35.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,220)}I. 人员变动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:39.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,1996年，在id放弃了《雷神之锤》，开除了John Romero之后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.16,0:00:41.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们正在为下一个游戏寻找创意上的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.88,0:00:43.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个游戏不是一开始就叫做《雷神之锤II》的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:47.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当时还有其他的想法，诸如WOR等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:49.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过他们还是起名为《雷神之锤II》了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:51.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,虽然和首作没啥关系就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:57.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,根据id的股东，以及在其中担任设计工作25年的Tim Willits
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.42,0:00:59.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《雷神之锤》首作开发的过程可谓一团糟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:02.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以，大家决定要对游戏的开发有一个清晰的路线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.78,0:01:04.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那就是科幻风和宇宙飞船！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.51,0:01:06.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,先说一下，当时是1997年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.18,0:01:09.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,“魁梧难缠的太空战士”的说法还没过时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.26,0:01:11.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比如一个人为了爱兔而干翻地狱啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:14.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,开发者曾经借鉴了这部电影的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:14.90,Comments,,0,0,0,,注：The Guns of Navarone(纳瓦隆大炮)是1961年于美国上映的二战片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.90,0:01:16.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,电影是关于二战时期一个突击队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:19.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,被派遣毁坏敌方大炮，进而大英帝国海军
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:21.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,可以从纳粹那里救出被困士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.36,0:01:24.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我反正是没看过，这电影比我父母还老
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.74,0:01:29.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们在那期讲DOS啥的视频里，引述完某个更老的电影之后说的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.68,0:01:31.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那么，《雷神之锤II》的剧情嘛......
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.16,0:01:33.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，别太激动，这个游戏还是老样子，没多少剧情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:37.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,大多数是借鉴那个二战相关电影，而不是克苏鲁啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:37.44,Comments,,0,0,0,,注：Howard Phillips Lovecraft，美国恐怖、科幻与奇幻小说作家。\N他最著名的作品是后来被称为“克苏鲁神话”（Cthulhu Mythos）的一系列小说。\N大家也可以去听Metallica的The Call of Ktulu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.44,0:01:38.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并且从游戏开始，你会感受到较上一个作品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.90,0:01:42.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个游戏的目标更加明显，制作更精良，让人印象深刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:45.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而这就有点搞笑了，它或许是整个系列作里最少被人所提及的了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.56,0:01:47.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《雷神之锤》一代有那种特殊的灵魂，那种气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.68,0:01:50.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,很明显都是Trent Reznor制作的原声带所烘托的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.68,0:01:50.16,Comments,,0,0,0,,注：你们把Trent Reznor当作Nine Inch Nail就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:53.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,Trent Reznor被请回来，他看了游戏之后拒绝制作原声带
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:56.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,记得新闻报过，说他虽然想义务制作，但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:01:58.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1358,858)}“这个游戏没有那味了。”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:02:00.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得对于id来说，《雷神之锤II》算是一个转折点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:03.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他从一个制作了很多有重大影响游戏的，又破又小的公司
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.88,0:02:05.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,变成了一个真正的公司
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:06.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有很多有责任心的员工
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:10.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些人很好，很敬业，然而不像之前那样个性鲜明了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:13.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,更不必说Tom Hall和John Romero被开除后创建了Ion Storm
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:13.90,Comments,,0,0,0,,注：John Romero 的 Daikatana 可谓让其身败名裂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:16.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,Sandy Peterson去Ensemble Studios开发帝国时代去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:20.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而Civvie心中的完美大神以及能让Jace Hall窒息的辣个男人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:20.56,Comments,,0,0,0,,注：Jace Hall是一位制作人，参与了F.E.A.R的开发与发行，就是那个黑人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:22.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,“我要从后面向你发起进♂攻”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:28.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,“刚那感觉我这辈子头一回体验，你从摄像机回放看到了吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:29.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,“刚那下挺好的”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:30.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,“幸亏你的裤子还没湿掉”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:32.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这家伙开发了一个新引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.94,0:02:36.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,或者说，是把上一个Quake引擎改进了一下，变得更加彩色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:38.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是他没有实现骨骼动画
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:40.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他为啥不再多写点功能呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:43.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,无论如何，这俩人都还在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:45.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\pos(974,420)}美工兼创始人Adrian Carmack
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:45.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1052,888)}设计师American MaGee
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:44.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但对于id来说，却有点不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:48.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也许对于真正具有革命性的东西来说，真就是后浪拍前浪呗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:51.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一年后《半条命》和《虚幻》就上市了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:53.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当年可是按照“雷神之锤的终结者”的标准来开发的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:57.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得也是做到了，我觉得《虚幻》比《雷神之锤II》好玩多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:03:00.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我对《雷神之锤II》不是那么熟悉，不像一代《雷神之锤》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:04.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,或是《毁灭战士》，《毁灭战士III》，乃至《德军总部3D》
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:07.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但我还是对最高难度会是啥样很感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:10.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,原版《雷神之锤II》没法让你选择最高难度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:12.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也就是第三难度，通称“困难+”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:16.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,万幸的是，我用的改进引擎将其命名为“噩梦难度”，并可以选择
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:16.86,Comments,,0,0,0,,注：《雷神之锤II》引擎于2001年11月开源
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:18.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得，对于带动我的精力来说，还挺管用的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:22.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为我经常在Ammo Depot这关厌倦了，然后弃游了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:27.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我当然通关了，而且这游戏还是我第一个在网上死斗的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:28.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,多人死斗模式真是好玩得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:31.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我在死之前永远想不起来电磁炮在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:35.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,最高难度就是这样，因为我经常被高手欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:38.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,经常被这个恶霸打死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:40.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,最高难度和困难难度大致相同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:43.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是敌人不会退缩，攻击更快，而且血量更多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:46.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,大多数时候我都体会不到，除了这里......
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:50.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,没错，我记住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:55.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,无论如何，我该开始这段不那么奇怪的旅程了，体会id的黑暗时光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:58.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然，这不意味着《雷神之锤II》是个差劲的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:04:01.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得id在此之后发布的游戏都差不多这个风格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,直到《毁灭战士2016》和《毁灭战士：永恒》
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:05.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,没错，《毁灭战士：永恒》打磨得很复杂精细
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:08.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我都想不到这公司还能再次做出如此让人印象深刻的游戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:11.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《毁灭战士2016》算是id风格的进化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:14.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《毁灭战士：永恒》就是再次定义了这个流派的无限可能性了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:16.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然而《雷神之锤II》在发掘可能性方面就差点意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:22.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,科幻风很好，一个好的动作游戏，并且到处血肉横飞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:26.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,再说，《雷神之锤II》要是这个公司出的最差游戏的话，那也没啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:26.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过RAGE更差:-(
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:26.98,Comments,,0,0,0,,注：id公司于2011出品的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:29.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,天啊，要说到RAGE......
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:34.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,“我们山上的广播塔停止工作了，我们得找人修一下”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:37.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,“应该只是哪个部件需要对齐一下”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:41.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,“你给我修好了，我就给你把霰弹枪，祝你好运”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,“这活应该不难”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:04.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,“干得不错，陌生人！”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:10.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,190)}II. 游戏原声
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,哇，我能先说游戏原声吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:11.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为真是好听得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:13.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他不是Trent Reznor制作的那种恐怖氛围音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:17.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,又重又硬，完美的重金属。正是Bobby Prince想做的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:20.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过这个可以刻进CD,在游戏里欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:21.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,真是好极～了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:24.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些音乐由Sonic Mayhem编曲，他的真名嘛......
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:26.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我都不知道我该怎么读:-P
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:29.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,像这种音乐，我们可以直接插进CD播放机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:30.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,(当时我们经常这么干)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:32.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后可以在不玩游戏的时候欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:35.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,真的很干脆利落，给游戏增添了很多动力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:58.09,Comments,,0,0,0,,BGM: Quad Machine by Sonic Mayhem
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:06:00.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,200)}III. 血与铁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:02.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,游戏的大致剧情是，你是Bitterman
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:04.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好家伙，主角居然有个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:18.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你的吊仓在Stroggos族的星球上坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:22.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,Stroggos族十分邪恶，将人类或是外星人啥的焊接上钢铁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:24.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有点像赛博人，不过更加暴力，野蛮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:26.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且还能爆炸:-P
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:28.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且只有一类有护盾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:32.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你主要的任务，除去那些整个游戏里都有的分支任务外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:33.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就是去摧毁大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:33.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就是去摧毁{\fs100}大{\fs75}炮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:34.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就是去摧毁{\fs100}大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:34.40,Comments,,0,0,0,,Brian Johnson *1
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:39.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你进入了一个军事设施，然后城市，又一个军事设施，最后是宫殿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:42.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《雷神之锤II》在关卡交互上没啥多样性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:43.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,基本上按下后就是那些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.76,0:06:46.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,尽管关卡设计中实现了《毁灭巫师》那样的多地图系统
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:49.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,可以让你在前后关卡之间无缝穿梭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:52.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过这没有在什么重要步骤方面使用，你走进了这个地图
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:55.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后完成了一项任务，开起之前地图的某个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你走了进去，然后你完成任务后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:59.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你也许都不知道你完成了一项任务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:01.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为你需要干的事情过于熟悉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:04.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也许我玩得很多了，但是当你和Strogg战斗的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:05.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,任务之间的关系就能串起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:10.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我从未迷糊过，也许这就体现出关卡设计师们的经验丰富了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:14.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,游戏的第一个部分就是你坠机后，你爬出来吊仓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:16.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你看到了这个场景，手里只有爆能枪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:18.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,威力只够打死几个小怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:22.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,大约一分钟后，你得到了霰弹枪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:33.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这霰弹枪还算可以，我喜欢它的外观，尽管有点不得劲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:35.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,游戏还告诉你玻璃可以打碎呢:-|
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:38.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你可以蹲下，还有一个电子合成声音告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:39.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,“任务已更新”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:42.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当你的任务状态改变的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:44.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你立刻感觉到这可不是初代《雷神之锤》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:48.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果你足够幸运，在当年有3D加速卡的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这看起来也不像初代《雷神之锤》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:53.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,尽管软件渲染下，光照效果和粒子效果挺让人印象深刻的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过光追版就很垃圾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:08:00.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,跑起来不流畅，而且就连T.Reznor提到的那点没有的气氛都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:02.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,默认设置下，所有东西看起来都太亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:04.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果关闭这些效果的话，你还要解决贴图错误
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:07.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且他们改的电磁炮是什么玩意？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:09.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,每个东西都很亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:12.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为加载了并非为其设计的高清材质包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过至少是免费的:-P
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.76,Comments,,0,0,0,,注：https://github.com/NVIDIA/Q2RTX
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:15.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有一个新玩意，就是储物系统
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:18.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你第一次拾起来的东西是消声器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:22.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然，有用的东西也有。四倍伤害，无敌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:26.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有防护衣，整个游戏也就三个地方有用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:28.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有一个超级护甲，就这样......吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.56,0:08:33.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我攒着这些道具，等到需要的时候再用，多数情况是打Boss
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:36.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过可惜的是，你在二代游戏中拿到的四倍伤害比一代时要少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:38.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而rampage就更少了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:43.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,貌似整个游戏最多见到一两个，看上去也无关紧要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:46.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就像《毁灭战士2016》那样，整场大战下来没捡起多少东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:24.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《雷神之锤II》的确有那种气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:27.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那种不详的科幻气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:31.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,血与铁所铸就的太空坏蛋，很明显受到了那部电影的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:32.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,敌人也不退缩，步步紧逼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:35.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过他们在死的时候仍然在尝试攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:37.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然，为避免这种现象，你可以将其打爆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:44.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你没听错，他们都能打爆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:46.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他 们 都 能 打 爆！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:48.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,真心觉得很酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:50.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你穿过基地，射杀Strogg们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:52.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们不会给你多少麻烦，直到你见到了Enforcers
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:54.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有机关枪呀，好吧:-P
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:58.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在下关拿到小型机关枪后，稍微好对付了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:58.16,Comments,,0,0,0,,SuperBart: 应该是minigun，怀疑原作者口误
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过这枪还带反冲的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:01.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你游戏设计师没事搞这些干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:02.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,把刚那段剪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:08.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,虽然玩起来还是很愉快，因为游戏很早就给你这把枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:22.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但这把枪可不是全部，我们需要去秘密关卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:23.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,只要我们经过下水道:-P
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:26.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,游个泳，上个电梯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:30.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你的任务就由“做一些大致能对拯救人类有意义的事情”变成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:31.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,“找到一个有威力的武器”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,啊这......那就找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:48.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《雷神之锤II》的超级霰弹枪算是继承了家族之光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:52.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在是泵动式的了，听起来和《毁灭战士二》的一样，具有毁灭性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.68,0:10:55.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而这也能体现出这个游戏的武器都很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.68,0:10:55.86,Comments,,0,0,0,,SuperBart: 我们辅导员说我们大类的专业都很不错，可是我不想去人工智能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:59.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然，不知为啥，枪口也没有闪光，不过没啥关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:02.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你也拿到了手榴弹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:05.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过我不经常使用，我攒着它，等有榴弹发射器的时候再用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:09.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在“困难”模式下，你会在游戏的第一部分见到两个最危险的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:14.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,天哪，这玩意真是腻味死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.68,0:11:16.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他会吸干你的体力，使用了......
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:17.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,:-(
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:22.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有Gunner，也就在“困难+”难度下有点困难，因为他攻击得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:25.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我也不知道他会朝我开枪，还是扔手榴弹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:29.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,游戏开始，如果你离手榴弹很近的话，你可以蹲下来，以减少伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:32.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过我更乐意在之后，用火箭发射器或电磁炮来消灭他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:34.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在这之前，只能用超级霰弹枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:38.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我想说一点，这些设计没一个是“坏设计”，至少肯定是千锤百炼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:42.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你的敌人都能发出挺不错的音效，也有动作来给玩家合适的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:45.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你走近了一个房间，你听到了某些东西，你意识到可能要出事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:47.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,“阻挡一切！”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:47.18,Comments,,0,0,0,,注：这玩意官方名字为Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:51.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这家伙就是纸打的老虎，也就叫得响
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:54.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他攻击时摆臂时间过长，所以你要被打到的话，该练练反应能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:59.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你在第一部分也能看到其他的敌人，诸如这两个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:01.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,拿超级霰弹枪很快就能处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:05.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得除了开始说的那两个，其他的敌人都没那么烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:06.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们处理起来都不难
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:09.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,敌人也有很多很酷的默认动画
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:12.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过在游戏中很难看到，毕竟一直在开枪打怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:24.82,Comments,,0,0,0,,阿姨，您多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:27.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你小子叫吗?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:27.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,"毁坏者!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:30.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你有兄弟姐妹吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:32.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,等会......这是个僵尸:-P
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:34.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,算了吧，下次再得嘞你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:38.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还记得我说过，我在Ammo Depot这关由于太厌倦而弃坑了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:40.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，游戏的第二部分开始就是这关
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:42.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我也一直在想为啥我会厌倦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:47.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你开始就能拿到机关枪，挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:49.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,尽管这玩意太费子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也许就是其贼耗子弹才有的爽快感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:55.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我想不起来有啥FPS游戏让你能在一个敌人上面倾泻那么多的子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:58.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,虽然老这么做很不现实，但是还是很爽快的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:13:04.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但你经常走进一个屋子，在5秒内打出200个子弹，把敌人都打爆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:05.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,真的很让人满足
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:18.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,270)}IV. 还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:19.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个地方经常能让我弃游
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:20.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过为何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:23.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是因为我已经打通了最高难度了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:24.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这游戏可不这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:27.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也不知为嘛，这游戏把这些Tank当成很难对付的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:31.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过我可以一直用机关枪打他，并躲避所有火箭和能量波
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:33.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得第一个Boss更适合被叫做Tank
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:34.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你看看这玩意！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:51.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,要讲这个游戏每个部分都是干啥的话，就有些无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:55.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在其他游戏中，你会遇到很多其他关卡，可以争取更高的分数
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:59.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个游戏感觉像是在一直坚持某种特定的复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:02.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,确实不差，但根本没有脱颖而出的特点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:05.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以接下来的节目中，我要介绍其他的枪了，因为他们太好用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:09.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,先是榴弹发射器，我觉得手感比一代和三代的好得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:12.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而火箭发射器比一代差劲一点，不过还好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:15.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,高速爆能枪不知为啥，枪口还能旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:18.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过我觉得这玩意能代替机关枪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:20.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就是很标准的快射速能量枪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:22.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,电磁炮十分完美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:25.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也许Shadow Warrior先有的，不过《雷神之锤II》的最好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:29.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《雷神之锤III》的加入了一系列声音，提醒玩家可以再次发炮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:34.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,挺好的，要不然我觉得雷神之锤系列的电磁炮也就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:39.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有BFG10K，一听就知道这是干啥的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:42.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,头一回升级传统的BFG9K
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:45.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,显得和之前毁灭战士的那玩意没啥关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:50.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他射出一个大绿球，空中飞行的同时还对其附近的敌人发射激光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:53.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而这就算是“id军械库”的所有内容了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:55.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,基本上id的游戏或多或少都会遵循的惯例
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:59.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,直到《毁灭战士2016》，会给你一个霰弹枪或是电磁炮啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:00.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,手枪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:01.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,霰弹枪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:02.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,超级霰弹枪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:04.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,轻型自动化武器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.74,0:15:06.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,重型自动化武器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:07.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,火箭发射器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:09.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,快射速能量枪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:10.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,（《雷神之锤III》有两种）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:11.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,电磁炮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:12.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有BFG
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:16.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就这些了，简直像个标杆，可称之为id标杆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:18.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得就是这点，让我耿耿于怀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:20.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也是为啥这个游戏让我觉得心里很拧巴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:22.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,id已然是个标杆了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:25.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而对于这种游戏模式，他们倒是会有微调
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:28.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《毁灭战士3》是恐怖风格，Rage有三条支线任务
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:33.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就好像游戏除了技术革新，游戏性没啥变化了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:33.36,Comments,,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(498,94)} DOOM3引擎(id Tech 4)：光影效果\NRage 引擎(id Tech 5)：大贴图快速加载
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:36.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而技术的开发可谓拖了游戏开发的后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:39.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《毁灭战士3》花了4年，而Rage花了7年!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:42.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,id一直是，而且将永远是一个技术先行者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:45.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我本想和我做过的其他游戏介绍视频一样，介绍这个游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:48.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,敌人长这样，武器是这些，他们是这样组合的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:49.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但你们早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:52.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,游戏中有一些秘密关卡，Sudden Death实际上很独特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:55.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你在Receiving Center这关跳过这个瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:57.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你就会被带到Sudden Death
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:16:01.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在很短的时间内收集尽量多的增强道具和武器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:03.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,快到游戏结尾时，有第三个秘密关卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:06.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是一个低重力太空站，全都是飞行怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:18.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,真就这味呗:-P
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,再玩一次《雷神之锤II》也没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:22.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但你要是问我游戏哪里很精彩的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:23.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我没啥可说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:28.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,Mine关有很多Mutants，有三个Boss，都不难处理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:30.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且这三个Boss也没多大区别
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:35.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有一个坦克，有一个能飞，最终Boss有两种类型的BFG
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:40.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我把《雷神之锤II》通关了，花了我小6个小时记笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:42.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而笔记很快就能看完......
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:59.66,Comments,,0,0,0,,{\pos(936,269)}"高速爆能枪跟机关枪差不多，不过更容易瞄准"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:59.66,Comments,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1446,408)}"好用的远距离武器在游戏开始没有"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:59.66,Comments,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1368,481)}"游戏原声很好听"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:59.66,Comments,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1374,555)}"没被触发的敌人更好杀"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:59.66,Comments,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1500,873)\fs50}"注意Strogg读音，否则有人钻牛角尖"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:16:59.66,Comments,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1266,925)}"Torture chambers那关真不好玩"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:01.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,Torture chambers 经常让我陷入困境
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:03.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我所注意到的最困难的一关
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:04.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就算遇见了Iron Maidens，也不是事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:08.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,很快就能处理掉，俩火箭或两枪电磁炮就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:11.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是过道很危险，甚至有个小型下水道环节:-P
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:13.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,里面有一个Parasite
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.37,0:17:16.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就好像他们知道23年后，会有人来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:18.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,将其作为一个差劲包袱录进视频，我还逃不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:20.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果我不这么做的话，就没啥笑话了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:25.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为我每次得费老大劲数清每一个下水道环节
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:37.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得当我们接近大炮的时候，事情就明显了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:37.68,Comments,,0,0,0,,Brian Johnson * 2
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且还有空袭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:07.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我按照指示，摧毁了Strogg的补给火车
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:10.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我不知那里面有啥，任务有啥重要的，不过没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,《雷神之锤II》的任务设计在描述
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:15.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,人类对Stroggos的任务上面还挺让人明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:20.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你孤军深入，其他人无法登陆，直至你摧毁了大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:20.20,Comments,,0,0,0,,Brain Johnson * 3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:23.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,为达成此目标，我们得完成一系列次要目标
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:26.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我对这场战争是如何开始的，表示不甚了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:26.22,Comments,,0,0,0,,SuperBart：所以有些小学生(非字面义)无故攻击这个，攻击那个，为啥呢:-(
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:28.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,游戏开始的引入部分倒是介绍了为啥我们受到了攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:33.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,开始的部分像新闻简报，说Strogg攻击了主要城市
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:35.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而我们的单人英雄正在和其鏖战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:35.32,Comments,,0,0,0,,SuperBart：瓦尔特保卫萨达热窝即视感？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:54.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,背景还行，那些外星混蛋会付出代价的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:58.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有点像《毁灭战士》和初代《雷神之锤》说明书中提到的正义大战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:00.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也就是你消灭游戏中一切生灵的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:02.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,过场动画是《雷神之锤II》的新特性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:04.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然而我觉得没啥用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:06.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,机器人声音告诉你任务
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:08.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,游戏两部分之间有电脑屏幕，和类似的机器人声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:11.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,展示地图，并告诉你接下来要做什么
