Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:39.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,又念Str-oag?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:42.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fnipix_12px\fs45\an4\c&38AF3D&\b1\pos(394,88)}已找到
